QUANTITY 7

MSG 00
Level 14
MSG_END

MSG 01
Notice there are two new instructions: CMP and JE
MSG_END

MSG 02
CMP compares two operands
 
Examples:
CMP rax, rbx
CMP rax, 4
MSG_END

MSG 03
CMP sets ZF to 1 when the operands are equal
MSG_END

MSG 04
CMP sets ZF to 0 when the operands are different
MSG_END

MSG 05
JE jumps if 
ZF = 1
Otherwise it continues to the next instruction
MSG_END

MSG 06
You will need CMP and JE to solve the challenge
MSG_END

