MSG 00
Level 15
MSG_END

MSG 01
Notice there is a new instruction: JNE (Jump if Not Equal)
MSG_END

MSG 02
JNE jumps if 
ZF = 0
Otherwise it continues to the next instruction
MSG_END

MSG 03
CMP sets ZF to 0 when the operands are different
MSG_END

MSG 04
CMP sets ZF to 1 when the operands are equal
MSG_END

